@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hjspkd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v1 + v2) * wp.exp((v1 + 0.50 - tmp + 0.31)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.32)) / (v2 / (tmp + 0.76 - tmp + 0.47)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
